            <title>[SOLR-3646] /browse request handler fails in example if you don&apos;t specify a field in the query with &quot;no default specified via &apos;df&apos; param&quot;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3646</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If you try using the stock /browse request handler and don&apos;t specify a field in the search, you get the following stack (partial):&lt;/p&gt;

